<div class="container">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text-color);">Daily Plan: Monday, January 10, 2026 (Week 2 Continuation: C.2 Model Audit + F.1 Planning)</h1>
    
    <div class="last-updated" style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">
        <strong>Context:</strong> Week 2 Day 2 focus | 
