    <h2>🔴 Priority 1: C.2 Model Audit - Phase 2 (3-4 hours)</h2>
    
    <p><strong>Continue Model Audit:</strong> Document remaining models (70+), dependencies, usage patterns, database schema.</p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Complete Model Documentation:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>File: /Documentation/C2_Model_Audit_Phase2_Report.tt</li>
                <li>Document: All remaining models with dependencies</li>
                <li>Include: Field descriptions, relationships, usage examples</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Identify gaps and improvements:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>List: Models missing documentation</li>
                <li>Flag: Potential schema inconsistencies</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p><strong>Expected Deliverable:</strong> Complete C.2 Model Audit Phase 2 report</p>

    <h2>🟠 Priority 2: F.1 Master Plan IDE Integration - Planning (2 hours)</h2>
    
    <p><strong>Plan IDE integration infrastructure:</strong> Prepare for coordinated project management in IDE.</p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Review current F.1 plan scope:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Read: MasterPlanCoordination.tt F.1 section</li>
                <li>Identify: IDE integration requirements</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Create F.1 Implementation Plan:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>File: /Documentation/F1_IDE_Integration_Plan.tt</li>
                <li>Include: Architecture, dependencies, timeline</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p><strong>Expected Deliverable:</strong> F.1 IDE Integration Planning document</p>

    <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; margin: 20px 0;">
